description: You have been temporarily jailed on our server due to suspicious activity. In order to continue participating, you must complete a verification process to confirm your identity.

To verify that you are not underage, not beyond our age limit (40 years old) and that you are not a catfish, please follow the instructions in the [**Verification Channel**](https://discord.com/channels/1349136661971206268/1349244585947299921).

If you believe you've already completed the verification process or need any assistance, please reach out to our team via the [**Support Channel**](https://discord.com/channels/1349136661971206268/1349244644247998516).
